#EVTDESC_KO_566;For the farewell ceremony townspeople crowd the shrines of the divine couple. The holy tree, along with its branch, is placed in the center as Mus secure the pledges of the populace in return for a great harvest. Many have travelled just to witness the burning of the sacred tree and thousands of paper flowers. At the close many pilgrims stay behind to buy commodities.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTA_KO_566;We all benefit.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTDESC_KO_567;A Mu is planning a performance but hasn't made her mind to which spirit flowers would be best to adorn the performance. This will also covertly sign to state officals the throne's policy.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTA_KO_567;Darihwa - the fantastical flower.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
