#EVTDESC_KO_568;A Mu-Dang asks you to help her pick a spirit flower for the street parade. It is ritual and because [From.GetTitledFirstName] is over deliberating a woman's touch might be needed.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTA_KO_568;Darihwa - the fantastical flower.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTA_KO_568_TT;Chases ghosts leaving villagers secure.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTB_KO_568;Mudonghwa - the child dancer flower.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTB_KO_568_TT;Ensures longevity for elderly;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
