#EVTDESC_KO_569;Tensions have grown as a Mu living in town is trading Wuzhu for Jijeon, spirit-world currency, at a cut-throat exchange rate. Her followers are now numerous and quite a number of Mu Dangs and Hwaraengi are considering an unholy alliance to chase her from town.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTA_KO_569;Declare her currency fake!;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTB_KO_569;Decide to have her exiled.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTC_KO_569;Bring her to court under royal protection.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTD_KO_569;Secretly support and invest in her.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTDESC_KO_569.1;The towns people have laughed at your attempt to overrule a shaman. This episode will spice up some local songs that list your character flaws.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTA_KO_569.1;Drats.;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTB_KO_569.1;Have her exiled!;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTOPTC_KO_569.1;Kill her followers and bring her to me!;;;;;;;;;;;;;x;;;;;;;;;;;;
#EVTDESC_KO_569.2;Because of your reknown for compassion and piety the Mu has found business in fake Jijeon's" very difficult. You expect some exagerated story celebrating this episode to soon appear in the more petty Mu-Dangs repetoires.
